

1.安装 bison

brew install bison
cd /Applications/Xcode.app/Contents/Developer/Toolchains/XcodeDefault.xctoolchain/usr/bin/
sudo mv bison bison_under3
sudo scp /usr/local/Cellar/bison/3.0.4/bin/bison ./

2.安装 libevent

2.1 安装 openssl http://mac-dev-env.patrickbougie.com/openssl/
2.2 安装 libevent http://mac-dev-env.patrickbougie.com/libevent/

http://mac-dev-env.patrickbougie.com/


3.安装 thrift

http://thrift.apache.org/docs/install/os_x




sudo mkdir -p /usr/local/mac-dev-env  环境目录  
sudo mkdir -p /usr/local/src  原文件目录
sudo mkdir -p /usr/local/var/log 日志目录